data.description: THIS HOME HAS AN ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE WITH A LOW INTEREST RATE. Here we have a 3 bedroom/2 bath home with an attached heated garage & an additional detached garage. This home sits on 28 acres and has 771 ft of Kettle River shoreline. The home has a huge main bedroom w/ private bath, 2 more good sized bedrooms, a large living room, with an extra office area that includes a propane fireplace, huge kitchen with a dining area, breakfast bar, ample cabinet space & an island. From the dining area there is a sliding glass door that leads to a large deck and screened in porch that overlooks the groomed backyard leading to the river. The property has trails by the river & a wildlife pond. There is also a deer stand that has been successful over the years. The fields on the front side of the property have just been turned & will have new planting done in the spring. If you are looking for a private, secluded river home with excellent hunting and plenty of storage, take a look at this one.
